---
/* FoodMaking.astro */
---

<section class="bg-pastel py-36 px-6 md:px-16 lg:px-24">
  <!-- Título -->
  <div class="text-center mb-14">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-burdeaux mb-6">
      Le Nostre Specialità
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl mb-16">
      Riscopri i sapori autentici dell’Emilia
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Grid -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">

    <!-- Tigelle -->
    <div class="bg-white shadow-md overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
      <div class="relative">
        <img
          src="/assets/fotos/FoodMaking/03.webp"
          alt="Tigelle fatte a mano viste da vicino"
          class="w-full h-60 object-cover"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-burdeaux/40 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
        <h3 class="absolute bottom-3 left-5 text-white text-2xl font-semibold">
          Tigelle
        </h3>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 flex flex-col justify-between flex-1">
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
               Le tigelle, piccoli dischi di pane cotti tra piastre roventi, sono
              un'icona della cucina modenese. Servite calde e fumanti, perfette da
              farcire con affettati locali, formaggi e il tradizionale pesto modenese.
       </p>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 pt-2 text-burdeaux">
          <!-- Wheat icon -->
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-wheat-icon lucide-wheat w-8 h-8 text-burdeaux" fill="currentColor"><path d="M2 22 16 8"/><path d="M3.47 12.53 5 11l1.53 1.53a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 4.94L5 19l-1.53-1.53a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0-4.94Z"/><path d="M7.47 8.53 9 7l1.53 1.53a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 4.94L9 15l-1.53-1.53a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0-4.94Z"/><path d="M11.47 4.53 13 3l1.53 1.53a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 4.94L13 11l-1.53-1.53a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0-4.94Z"/><path d="M20 2h2v2a4 4 0 0 1-4 4h-2V6a4 4 0 0 1 4-4Z"/><path d="M11.47 17.47 13 19l-1.53 1.53a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.94 0L5 19l1.53-1.53a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.94 0Z"/><path d="M15.47 13.47 17 15l-1.53 1.53a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.94 0L9 15l1.53-1.53a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.94 0Z"/><path d="M19.47 9.47 21 11l-1.53 1.53a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.94 0L13 11l1.53-1.53a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.94 0Z"/>
        </svg>

          <span class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold">
            Impasto tradizionale fatto in casa
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Crescentine -->
    <div class="bg-white shadow-md overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
      <div class="relative">
        <img
          src="/assets/fotos/FoodMaking/06.webp"
          alt="Crescentine emiliane fatte in casa"
          class="w-full h-60 object-cover"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-burdeaux/40 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
        <h3 class="absolute bottom-3 left-5 text-white text-2xl font-semibold">
          Crescentine
        </h3>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 flex flex-col justify-between flex-1">
        <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Le crescentine, conosciute anche come "gnocco fritto", sono mezzelune di
              pasta fritta che si gonfiano durante la cottura. Croccanti fuori e
              morbide dentro, accompagnano perfettamente salumi e formaggi della nostra
              terra.
       </p>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 pt-2 text-burdeaux">
          <!-- Utensils icon -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-utensils-icon lucide-utensils w-8 h-8 text-burdeaux" fill="currentColor"><path d="M3 2v7c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h4a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V2"/><path d="M7 2v20"/><path d="M21 15V2a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v6c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h3Zm0 0v7"/>
            </svg>

          <span class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold">
            Fritte al momento, sempre fresche
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
